  "Description": {
    "English": "Sideloads a <span class=\"name name-special\">resonant memory packet</span> into your warp computer,  allowing the ship to pass through the dissonant space surrounding <span class=\"name name-special\">purple stellar bodies</span>.<br><br>User is advised to access Hyperdrive systems via the <VAL_ON>Galactic Map<>.",
